{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb56764ac-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s1115"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1115"},"text":"§ 1115.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" TSA personnel limitations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any statutory limitation on the number of employees in the Transportation Security Administration does not apply to employees carrying out this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb56764ad-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/53/tXIII/s1306"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–53, title XIII, § 1306","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2007-08-03"},"text":"Aug. 3, 2007","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/121/395"},"text":"121 Stat. 395","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb56764ae-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb56764af-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idb56764b0-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original a reference to titles XII, XIII, XIV, and XV of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/53"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–53","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this chapter, amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s1992"},"text":"section 1992 of Title 18","children":[],"tail":", Crimes and Criminal Procedure, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t46/s70105"},"text":"section 70105 of Title 46","children":[],"tail":", Shipping, and sections 114, 5103a, 14504, 20106, 20109, 24301, 28101, 31105, and 46301 of Title 49, Transportation, enacted provisions set out as notes under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s1101"},"text":"section 1101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and sections 114, 13908, and 14504 of Title 49, and amended provisions set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s14504"},"text":"section 14504 of Title 49","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of titles XII to XV to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
